components.message: Make sure to rerun the script after changing the parameters here, otherwise they will not update in Python

components.text: [left][size=15]Specify here the amount of days before the due date, when you want to be warned about a possible delay. This should be a time where your standard item is already in the process but you still have time to take action to prevent delays. [/size][/left]

formula.text:
CASE WHEN ISNULL(<%=due_date%>)=1 THEN NULL 
    
         WHEN ISNULL(PU_LAST(VBAP,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.ACTIVITY_EN = <%=real_date%>))=1 AND
              HOURS_BETWEEN(<%=due_date%>,TO_TIMESTAMP('<%=today_help%>','YYYY-MM-DD')) >= (24.0 + 24.0* <%=buffer%>) THEN NULL
              
         WHEN ISNULL(PU_LAST(VBAP,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.ACTIVITY_EN = <%=real_date%>))=1 THEN ROUND(DAYS_BETWEEN(TO_TIMESTAMP('<%=today_help%>','YYYY-MM-DD'),<%=due_date%>))
         
        ELSE NULL END

formula.name: Single KPI
formula.text:
SUM(CASE WHEN 
    CASE WHEN ISNULL(<%=due_date%>)=1 THEN NULL 
    
         WHEN ISNULL(PU_LAST(VBAP,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.ACTIVITY_EN = <%=real_date%>))=1 AND
              HOURS_BETWEEN(<%=due_date%>,TO_TIMESTAMP('<%=today_help%>','YYYY-MM-DD')) >= (24.0 + 24.0* <%=buffer%>) THEN 1
              
         WHEN ISNULL(PU_LAST(VBAP,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.ACTIVITY_EN = <%=real_date%>))=1 THEN 2
         
         WHEN HOURS_BETWEEN(<%=due_date%>,PU_LAST(VBAP,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.ACTIVITY_EN = <%=real_date%>)) >= (24.0 + 24.0* <%=buffer%>) THEN 1
         
         WHEN HOURS_BETWEEN(<%=due_date%>,PU_LAST(VBAP,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.ACTIVITY_EN = <%=real_date%>)) < (24.0 + 24.0* <%=buffer%>) THEN 0
         
         ELSE 3 END =2 
         
         THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN ISNULL ( PU_FIRST ( "VBAP" , "VBEP"."TS_EDATU" , "VBEP"."ETENR" = '0001' ) ) = 1 AND ISNULL ( PU_LAST ( "VBAP" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Record Goods Issue' ) ) = 1 THEN 'no due date' WHEN ISNULL ( PU_FIRST ( "VBAP" , "VBEP"."TS_EDATU" , "VBEP"."ETENR" = '0001' ) ) = 1 THEN 'no due date' WHEN ISNULL ( PU_LAST ( "VBAP" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Record Goods Issue' ) ) = 1 AND HOURS_BETWEEN ( PU_FIRST ( "VBAP" , "VBEP"."TS_EDATU" , "VBEP"."ETENR" = '0001' ) , TO_TIMESTAMP( '2009-12-30' , 'YYYY-MM-DD' ) ) >= ( 24.0 + 24.0 * 1 ) THEN 'delayed' WHEN ISNULL ( PU_LAST ( "VBAP" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Record Goods Issue' ) ) = 1 THEN 'open' WHEN HOURS_BETWEEN ( PU_FIRST ( "VBAP" , "VBEP"."TS_EDATU" , "VBEP"."ETENR" = '0001' ) , PU_LAST ( "VBAP" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Record Goods Issue' ) ) >= ( 24.0 + 24.0 * 1 ) THEN 'delayed' WHEN HOURS_BETWEEN ( PU_FIRST ( "VBAP" , "VBEP"."TS_EDATU" , "VBEP"."ETENR" = '0001' ) , PU_LAST ( "VBAP" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Record Goods Issue' ) ) < ( 24.0 + 24.0 * 1 ) THEN 'not_delayed' ELSE NULL END AS "Status"

axis0.name: Status
axis0.text:
CASE WHEN ISNULL(<%=due_date%>)=1 AND ISNULL(PU_LAST(VBAP,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.ACTIVITY_EN = <%=real_date%>))=1 THEN 'no due date'
    
         WHEN ISNULL(<%=due_date%>)=1 THEN 'no due date'
    
         WHEN ISNULL(PU_LAST(VBAP,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.ACTIVITY_EN = <%=real_date%>))=1 AND
              HOURS_BETWEEN(<%=due_date%>,TO_TIMESTAMP('<%=today_help%>','YYYY-MM-DD')) >= (24.0 + 24.0* <%=buffer%>) THEN 'delayed'
              
         WHEN ISNULL(PU_LAST(VBAP,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.ACTIVITY_EN = <%=real_date%>))=1 THEN 'open'
         
         WHEN HOURS_BETWEEN(<%=due_date%>,PU_LAST(VBAP,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.ACTIVITY_EN = <%=real_date%>)) >= (24.0 + 24.0* <%=buffer%>) THEN 'delayed'
         
         WHEN HOURS_BETWEEN(<%=due_date%>,PU_LAST(VBAP,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME,_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES.ACTIVITY_EN = <%=real_date%>)) < (24.0 + 24.0* <%=buffer%>) THEN 'not_delayed'
         
         ELSE NULL END

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN ISNULL ( PU_FIRST ( "VBAP" , "VBEP"."TS_EDATU" , "VBEP"."ETENR" = '0001' ) ) = 1 THEN NULL WHEN ISNULL ( PU_LAST ( "VBAP" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Record Goods Issue' ) ) = 1 AND HOURS_BETWEEN ( PU_FIRST ( "VBAP" , "VBEP"."TS_EDATU" , "VBEP"."ETENR" = '0001' ) , TO_TIMESTAMP( '2009-12-30' , 'YYYY-MM-DD' ) ) >= ( 24.0 + 24.0 * 1 ) THEN NULL WHEN ISNULL ( PU_LAST ( "VBAP" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Record Goods Issue' ) ) = 1 THEN DAYS_BETWEEN ( TO_TIMESTAMP( '2009-12-30' , 'YYYY-MM-DD' ) , PU_FIRST ( "VBAP" , "VBEP"."TS_EDATU" , "VBEP"."ETENR" = '0001' ) ) ELSE NULL END AS "Reaction Time"
